  <ul>
    <li>Seamless display of components with structured formatting.</li>
    <li>Real-time HTML and component setting adjustments.</li>
    <li>Interactive configuration for component behavior and appearance.</li>
    <li>Plugin support for extended functionality.</li>
    <li>Instant preview of adjustments with live updates.</li>
    <li>Support for core components and optional plugins.</li>
    <li>Organized, reusable component architecture.</li>
    <li>Access to comprehensive documentation and guides.</li>
  </ul>
</div>


